<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA77">
<l>aṭipēriṟ pātāḷam pēru maṭikaṇ</l>
<l>muṭipēriṉ māmukaṭu pēruṅ - kaṭaka</l>
<l>maṟintāṭu kaipēriṉ vāṉṟicaikaḷ pēru</l>
<l>maṟintāṭu māṟṟā taraṅku</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When [his] foot moves the netherworld moves. When</l>
<l>the crown of Him moves the big roof moves. When [his] hands</l>
<l>move so that the bracelets dance upside down, the directions of the sky move.</l>
<l>He dances knowingly. The scene does not bear [it].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
